Keep an eye out for when we announce our Preorders, and stay updated on our Twitter and Instagram pages!

tags: My finals have been over for a week but ive reread his whole paper twice
I cant convince myself that it isint about fanfiction
title: Is...
body:
Arjun Appadurai… in this hella lengthy and esoteric reading about globalization for a 400 level undergraduate Anthropology Seminar… talking about…

fanfiction, covers, headcanons, fanart…

… fandom and stuff?

                                             Oh yes, he is.

From: Disjuncture and Difference in the Global Cultural Economy. (If you google it you can find a free access version on arjunappadurai.org)

summary: Fandom: Boku no Hero Academia Characters: Shinso Hitoshi, UA Teachers, Recovery Girl Warnings: depends if you want to do this as...
body:
Fandom: Boku no Hero Academia
Characters: Shinso Hitoshi, UA Teachers, Recovery Girl
Warnings: depends if you want to do this as a villain with a quirk or a disease

Prompt: Shinso Hitoshi has been having some strange dreams that make him reluctant to sleep, though he can’t seem to figure out why. He reluctantly explains to a teacher who brings him to Recovery Girl. Tests are done and nothing seems to be wrong so they decide to try sleeping aids, something different than he usually takes. He doesn’t wake up the next morning.

- kunnskat on AO3
